♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
00:00:32,060 --> 00:00:37,580
[Miss Mystery]

12
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:44,020
[Eighteen years ago, Xue Manor]

13
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:35,140
[Xue Manor suffered an unexpected fire.
The entire family perished in the blaze.]

14
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:42,060
[None of the family of three survived,
not even the servants.]

15
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:46,580
[Episode 1]

16
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,160
This way, please.

17
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,440
[Eighteen years later, Zhu Manor]

18
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,040
Hello.

19
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,120
Welcome.

20
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:53,280
[The Zhus]

21
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,640
This way, please.

22
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,480
What should we do now?

23
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,680
Guanwen's engagement banquet
is about to begin shortly.

24
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,600
Say something, please!

25
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,360
Master!

26
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,480
Madam!

27
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:04,280
I looked everywhere
and I can't find Mr. Zhu Jr.

28
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,000
Did you go check in the Blooming House?

29
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,600
Bloo...

30
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,200
Blooming House...

31
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,320
Not yet.

32
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,040
Go look for him now!

33
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:12,020
[Blooming House]

34
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,880
I think she went that way!

35
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:51,620
[Zhu Guanwen,
son of the richest men in Lianhe Town]

36
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,200
Who is this?

37
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:23,980
[Lin Bao'er, daughter of a rich merchant
in Southeast Asia]

38
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,000
(That's her.)

39
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:50,960
Where is she?

40
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:51,840
I think she went inside.

41
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:53,880
Open the door!

42
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,880
Who are you,
making loud noises at my door?

43
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,960
Don't disturb my fun time here.

44
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,360
You are still peeking, huh?

45
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,120
I'm so sorry, Sir.

46
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,800
Sorry!

47
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:10,760
My bad.

48
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,040
Let's go.

49
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,160
Thanks.

50
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,800
Are you just leaving like that?

51
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,200
I said "Thanks".

52
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,680
What else do you want from me?

53
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:31,000
At least I should know
who owes me a favor.

54
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,240
I'm Lin Bao'er.

55
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:34,360
Thank you for saving me.
I'll see you around.

56
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,320
Ms. Lin,

57
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,440
since you are here at the Blooming House,

58
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,200
don't pretend to be all pure and innocent.

59
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,960
(He took the bait.)

60
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,240
How overbearing, Mr. Zhu

61
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,760
This is so inappropriate.

62
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,600
After all, I don't throw myself to men.

63
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,040
If you want to have some fun with me,

64
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,800
I have to see if you, Mr. Zhu,

65
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,160
are charming enough.

66
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,120
Ms. Lin,

67
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,080
are you satisfied with my charm?

68
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,200
Too bad, I already have plans,

69
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,480
or I would spend some more time with you.

70
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:50,820
[Engagement Banquet Invitation]

71
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,920
Looks like

72
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,400
the main character is coming on stage.

73
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:07,360
Oh my, Master Zhu is indeed
the richest man in Lianhe Town.

74
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,720
His son's engagement banquet
looks quite impressive!

75
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,200
Mr. Zhu Jr. is marrying
the daughter of Mr. Dou, the mayor,

76
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,840
of course it needs to be grand.

77
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,480
But Mr. Zhu Jr. is still absent,

78
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,520
probably not willing to marry her at all.

79
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,040
How so?

80
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,760
The richest family allying with the mayor,

81
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:25,200
wouldn't that mean
the whole Lianhe Town belongs to the Zhus?

82
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,240
Let's wait and see
if Mr. Zhu Jr. will show up.

83
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,520
Sure, let's see.

84
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,800
Miss, this is
the engagement banquet of Mr. Zhu Jr.

85
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,760
We can't let you in
without the invitation.

86
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,080
I left it at home. Just let me in.

87
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,960
Sorry, you can't.

88
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:40,920
Please go back.

89
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,440
Please leave.

90
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:43,960
Mr. Zhu Jr.

91
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,440
(He finally arrived.)

92
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,960
Mr. Zhu Jr.

93
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,520
Ms. Lin,

94
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,560
we meet again!

95
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,040
Did you forget this?

96
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,180
[Engagement Banquet Invitation]

97
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,600
What took you so long?

98
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,640
I waited for so long.

99
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,920
(As expected, she left
the invitation there on purpose.)

100
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,120
Who is she?

101
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,520
I haven't seen her before.

102
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,680
Guanwen, you're finally here.

103
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,920
[Dou Lili, daughter of Lianhe Town's mayor]
Now everyone has arrived.

104
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,280
Who is this home-wrecker?

105
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,480
Lady, please pay attention to your words.

106
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:53,320
This is my engagement banquet.

107
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,080
You have no place to tell me what to do.

108
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,760
Ms. Dou,

109
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:59,160
She is an esteemed guest
invited by the Zhu family.

110
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,640
As the daughter of the town mayor,

111
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,120
please mind your manners.

112
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,600
Well,

113
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,720
Guanwen, you are here after all.

114
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,680
Looks like I'm disturbing you.

115
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,360
You purposely left the invitation there

116
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,920
in order to disturb me.

117
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,440
Ms. Lin, since you set the trap,

118
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,160
I should take the bait.

119
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,600
If you want to stir something up for me,

120
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,800
why don't we make it even bigger?

121
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,360
Mr. Zhu Jr., you finally showed up.

122
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,840
If you are still absent,
Master would punish me.

123
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,600
Let's go and change.

124
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,800
I'll be right back.

125
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,680
Guanwen, wait for me!

126
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:52,600
Miss!

127
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,400
I'm so sorry!

128
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,400
You clumsy hussy!

129
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:55,840
You won't be able to afford my dress

130
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,960
even if you work your butt off
for the rest of your life!

131
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,160
And you,

132
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,160
a random lowly woman,

133
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:07,000
how dare you pester Guanwen
and meddle in my business?

134
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,160
How dare you!

135
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,480
Master Zhu is here.

136
00:10:56,840 --> 00:11:01,160
I warmly welcome everyone
for attending the banquet today.

137
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,040
[Zhu Mao, the richest man of Lianhe Town]

138
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,680
[Second Madam Zhu, Lianhe Town]
Next, I would like to announce

139
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,760
a joyous occasion.

140
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,520
That is my son Zhu Guanwen's
engagement ceremony.

141
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:11,160
Guanwen and his fiancee...

142
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,840
Thank you all.

143
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,200
Thank you all.

144
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:20,400
Thank you all for taking time
out of your busy schedule

145
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,720
to come to my engagement banquet,

146
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:27,080
and witnessing
the most important moment of my life.

147
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:31,080
My fiancee is

148
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,800
a beauty

149
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,440
with grace

150
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,520
and intelligence.

151
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,360
Most importantly,

152
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,800
she has a righteous heart

153
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:45,000
which is fair and just.

154
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,360
It is my greatest honor

155
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:50,080
as Zhu Guanwen

156
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,320
to marry this woman.

157
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,880
Next,

158
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,240
I would like to proudly introduce

159
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:01,480
my fiancee,

160
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,240
the love of my life,

161
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,680
Ms. Lin, Lin Bao'er.

162
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:10,520
I thought it was Ms. Dou.

163
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,200
But what about Ms. Dou?

164
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,000
Now, this time,

165
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,360
are you satisfied?

166
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:27,940
♪That dangerous temptation♪

167
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:29,460
[Qian Tong, owner of the Shipping Company]

168
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:34,060
♪Like a moth darts into the flame♪

169
00:12:34,100 --> 00:12:36,180
♪Falling towards the light...♪

170
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:38,760
No!

171
00:12:38,780 --> 00:12:41,220
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

172
00:12:41,220 --> 00:12:43,140
[Dou Huaizhong, Lianhe Town's mayor]
[Yang Jian, detective chief]

173
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:48,380
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

174
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:50,780
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

175
00:12:50,820 --> 00:12:53,180
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

176
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:57,980
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

177
00:12:58,660 --> 00:13:03,020
♪Breaking free from
heavy shackles held tight♪

178
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:07,980
♪In the darkness a lone lamp glows♪

179
00:13:08,660 --> 00:13:13,020
♪Light and shadows
criss-cross in the night♪

180
00:13:13,380 --> 00:13:14,980
[Xue Manor suffered an unexpected fire.
The entire family perished in the blaze.]

181
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:18,500
♪No escape can yet be found♪

182
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:21,900
[None of the family of three survived,
not even the servants.]

183
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:28,700
♪On the bargaining table
right and wrong confound♪

184
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:32,940
♪See the raging fiery light♪

185
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:34,140
♪It will finally break free
from its plight♪

186
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:35,460
♪Flooding over everything in its wake♪

187
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:38,140
♪Escape it shall finally make♪

188
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:49,860
♪The end has now been reached♪

189
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:52,780
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

190
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:56,060
♪Looking away from you♪

191
00:13:56,060 --> 00:14:00,140
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

192
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:03,620
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

193
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:08,740
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

194
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:15,300
♪In a moment♪

195
00:14:15,340 --> 00:14:18,180
♪Flitting images flashing♪

196
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:20,580
♪Eyes fall shut♪

197
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:24,420
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

198
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,780
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

199
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,700
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

200
00:14:29,820 --> 00:14:35,980
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

201
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:39,780
♪In a moment♪

202
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:43,060
♪The memory in my mind♪

203
00:14:43,100 --> 00:14:44,700
♪Surging at me♪

204
00:14:44,740 --> 00:14:49,300
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

205
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:52,460
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

206
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:55,620
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

207
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:57,860
♪I may reopen my eyes♪
